---
// 404 placeholder UI per UI-SPEC lines 338-352
---

<section class="not-found">
  <div class="mascot-placeholder" role="img" aria-label="迷路的吉祥物"></div>
  <h1>咦？这里什么都没有…</h1>
  <p>迷路了？要不然回到首页吧</p>
  <a class="cta" href="/">回到首页</a>
</section>

<style>
  .not-found {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
  }
  .mascot-placeholder {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem auto;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-accent-subtle), var(--color-accent));
    border-radius: 24px;
  }
  .not-found h1 {
    color: var(--color-fg);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
  }
  .not-found p {
    color: var(--color-fg-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .not-found .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background var(--duration-fast) var(--easing-default);
  }
  .not-found .cta:hover,
  .not-found .cta:focus-visible {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }
</style>
